snippet.title: Contagion Review (beta) - Worth A Buy?
snippet.description:
Contagion is a cooperative survival horror FPS built on the latest Source Engine where players are forced to watch their ammo and aim carefully otherwise be overrun by the zombie hordes.  - That's great but is it worth a buy?
